{
  "video_id": "d0a0eXJ5TJM",
  "title": "The hidden opportunities of the informal economy | Niti Bhan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12901.0,
      "end_time": 16832.0,
      "text": "The informal markets of Africa are stereotypically seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16856.0,
      "end_time": 18703.0,
      "text": "as chaotic and lackadaisical."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19234.0,
      "end_time": 21887.0,
      "text": "The downside of hearing the word \"informal\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21911.0,
      "end_time": 24580.0,
      "text": "is this automatic grand association we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24604.0,
      "end_time": 26230.0,
      "text": "which is very negative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26254.0,
      "end_time": 30763.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s had significant consequences and economic losses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30787.0,
      "end_time": 36272.0,
      "text": "easily adding -- or subtracting -- 40 to 60 percent of the profit margin"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36297.0,
      "end_time": 39132.0,
      "text": "for the informal markets alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39157.0,
      "end_time": 43458.0,
      "text": "As part of a task of mapping the informal trade ecosystem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43483.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve done an extensive literature review"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46400.0,
      "end_time": 50991.0,
      "text": "of all the reports and research on cross-border trade in East Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51150.0,
      "end_time": 52826.0,
      "text": "going back 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52850.0,
      "end_time": 57184.0,
      "text": "This was to prepare us for fieldwork to understand what was the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57208.0,
      "end_time": 61370.0,
      "text": "what was holding back informal trade in the informal sector."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61990.0,
      "end_time": 65494.0,
      "text": "What we discovered over the last 20 years was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65518.0,
      "end_time": 69271.0,
      "text": "nobody had distinguished between illicit --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69295.0,
      "end_time": 73740.0,
      "text": "which is like smuggling or contraband in the informal sector --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73764.0,
      "end_time": 76104.0,
      "text": "from the legal but unrecorded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76128.0,
      "end_time": 79133.0,
      "text": "such as tomatoes, oranges, fruit."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79697.0,
      "end_time": 82170.0,
      "text": "This criminalization --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82410.0,
      "end_time": 87239.0,
      "text": "what in Swahili refers to as \"biashara,\" which is the trade or the commerce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87263.0,
      "end_time": 90697.0,
      "text": "versus \"magendo,\" which is the smuggling or contraband --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90721.0,
      "end_time": 94242.0,
      "text": "this criminalization of the informal sector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94266.0,
      "end_time": 98135.0,
      "text": "in English, by not distinguishing between these aspects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 98159.0,
      "end_time": 103752.0,
      "text": "easily can cost each African economy between 60 to 80 percent addition"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103776.0,
      "end_time": 106544.0,
      "text": "on the annual GDP growth rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 106568.0,
      "end_time": 110301.0,
      "text": "because we are not recognizing the engine"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110326.0,
      "end_time": 112899.0,
      "text": "of what keeps the economies running."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112924.0,
      "end_time": 116401.0,
      "text": "The informal sector is growing jobs at four times the rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 116425.0,
      "end_time": 118366.0,
      "text": "of the traditional formal economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 118391.0,
      "end_time": 120948.0,
      "text": "or \"modern\" economy, as many call it."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120972.0,
      "end_time": 124437.0,
      "text": "It offers employment and income generation opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 124462.0,
      "end_time": 128158.0,
      "text": "to the most \"unskilled\" in conventional disciplines."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 128183.0,
      "end_time": 131819.0,
      "text": "But can you make a french fry machine out of an old car?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 132403.0,
      "end_time": 135864.0,
      "text": "So, this, ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 135888.0,
      "end_time": 139104.0,
      "text": "is what so desperately needs to be recognized."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139128.0,
      "end_time": 143386.0,
      "text": "As long as the current assumptions hold that this is criminal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 143410.0,
      "end_time": 144637.0,
      "text": "this is shadow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 144661.0,
      "end_time": 146279.0,
      "text": "this is illegal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 146303.0,
      "end_time": 150763.0,
      "text": "there will be no attempt at integrating the informal economic ecosystem"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150787.0,
      "end_time": 153735.0,
      "text": "with the formal or even the global one."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 154968.0,
      "end_time": 157772.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to tell you a story of Teresia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 157796.0,
      "end_time": 161872.0,
      "text": "a trader who overturned all our assumptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 161896.0,
      "end_time": 165245.0,
      "text": "made us question all the stereotypes that we&#39;d gone in on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 165270.0,
      "end_time": 168176.0,
      "text": "based on 20 years of literature review."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169675.0,
      "end_time": 175164.0,
      "text": "Teresia sells clothes under a tree in a town called Malaba,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 175188.0,
      "end_time": 177284.0,
      "text": "on the border of Uganda and Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 177876.0,
      "end_time": 180450.0,
      "text": "You think it&#39;s very simple, don&#39;t you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180810.0,
      "end_time": 183467.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll go hang up new clothes from the branches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 183491.0,
      "end_time": 186423.0,
      "text": "put out the tarp, settle down, wait for customers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 186447.0,
      "end_time": 187792.0,
      "text": "and there we have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 187816.0,
      "end_time": 191201.0,
      "text": "She was everything we were expecting according to the literature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191225.0,
      "end_time": 192493.0,
      "text": "to the research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 192517.0,
      "end_time": 196293.0,
      "text": "right down to she was a single mom driven to trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 196318.0,
      "end_time": 197806.0,
      "text": "supporting her kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 199920.0,
      "end_time": 201702.0,
      "text": "So what overturned our assumptions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 201726.0,
      "end_time": 203245.0,
      "text": "What surprised us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 203269.0,
      "end_time": 206991.0,
      "text": "First, Teresia paid the county government market fees"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 207150.0,
      "end_time": 208845.0,
      "text": "every single working day"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208870.0,
      "end_time": 212123.0,
      "text": "for the privilege of setting up shop under her tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212147.0,
      "end_time": 214197.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s been doing it for seven years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 214222.0,
      "end_time": 216144.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s been getting receipts."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216560.0,
      "end_time": 218370.0,
      "text": "She keeps records."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 218610.0,
      "end_time": 221228.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re seeing not a marginal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221252.0,
      "end_time": 222599.0,
      "text": "underprivileged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 222623.0,
      "end_time": 228439.0,
      "text": "vulnerable African woman trader by the side of the road -- no."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 228463.0,
      "end_time": 232561.0,
      "text": "We were seeing somebody who&#39;s keeping sales records for years;"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 232586.0,
      "end_time": 238907.0,
      "text": "somebody who had an entire ecosystem of retail that comes in from Uganda"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 238931.0,
      "end_time": 241246.0,
      "text": "to pick up inventory;"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 241270.0,
      "end_time": 245132.0,
      "text": "someone who&#39;s got handcarts bringing the goods in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 245156.0,
      "end_time": 248720.0,
      "text": "or the mobile money agent who comes to collect cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 248960.0,
      "end_time": 249524.0,
      "text": "at the end of the evening."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 249548.0,
      "end_time": 253956.0,
      "text": "Can you guess how much Teresia spends, on average,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253980.0,
      "end_time": 256577.0,
      "text": "each month on inventory --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 256601.0,
      "end_time": 259274.0,
      "text": "stocks of new clothes that she gets from Nairobi?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 259819.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262900.0,
      "text": "One thousand five hundred US dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 262525.0,
      "end_time": 267965.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s around 20,000 US dollars invested in trade goods and services"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267989.0,
      "end_time": 269544.0,
      "text": "every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 269568.0,
      "end_time": 271180.0,
      "text": "This is Teresia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 271420.0,
      "end_time": 272438.0,
      "text": "the invisible one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272463.0,
      "end_time": 273743.0,
      "text": "the hidden middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 274442.0,
      "end_time": 278535.0,
      "text": "And she&#39;s only the first rung of the small entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 278559.0,
      "end_time": 282650.0,
      "text": "the micro-businesses that can be found in these market towns."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282674.0,
      "end_time": 287558.0,
      "text": "At least in the larger Malaba border, she&#39;s at the first rung."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 288523.0,
      "end_time": 291159.0,
      "text": "The people further up the value chain"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 291183.0,
      "end_time": 294228.0,
      "text": "are easily running three lines of business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 294252.0,
      "end_time": 299343.0,
      "text": "investing 2,500 to 3,000 US dollars every month."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 299772.0,
      "end_time": 303752.0,
      "text": "So the problem turned out that it wasn&#39;t the criminalization;"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 303776.0,
      "end_time": 308421.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t really criminalize someone you&#39;re charging receipts from."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 308957.0,
      "end_time": 314347.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the lack of recognition of their skilled occupations."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 315480.0,
      "end_time": 319440.0,
      "text": "The bank systems and structures have no means to recognize them"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 319680.0,
      "end_time": 320556.0,
      "text": "as micro-businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 320580.0,
      "end_time": 323157.0,
      "text": "much less the fact that, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323182.0,
      "end_time": 325390.0,
      "text": "her tree doesn&#39;t have a forwarding address."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325912.0,
      "end_time": 328238.0,
      "text": "So she&#39;s trapped in the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 328262.0,
      "end_time": 330693.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s falling through the cracks of our assumptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 330717.0,
      "end_time": 334256.0,
      "text": "You know all those microloans to help African women traders?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334646.0,
      "end_time": 337476.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to loan her 50 dollars or 100 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 337500.0,
      "end_time": 339106.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s she going to do with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 339130.0,
      "end_time": 341472.0,
      "text": "She spends 10 times that amount every month"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 341496.0,
      "end_time": 343970.0,
      "text": "just on inventory --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 343122.0,
      "end_time": 345409.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not talking about the additional services"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345433.0,
      "end_time": 347267.0,
      "text": "or the support ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 347864.0,
      "end_time": 351452.0,
      "text": "These are the ones who fit neither the policy stereotype"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351476.0,
      "end_time": 353880.0,
      "text": "of the low-skilled and the marginalized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 353904.0,
      "end_time": 356775.0,
      "text": "nor the white-collar, salaried office worker"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 356799.0,
      "end_time": 358659.0,
      "text": "or civil servant with a pension"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 358684.0,
      "end_time": 362560.0,
      "text": "that the middle classes are allegedly composed of."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 362800.0,
      "end_time": 366632.0,
      "text": "Instead, what we have here are the proto-SMEs"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 366656.0,
      "end_time": 370451.0,
      "text": "these are the fertile seeds of businesses and enterprises"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 370475.0,
      "end_time": 372418.0,
      "text": "that keep the engines running."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 372442.0,
      "end_time": 374177.0,
      "text": "They put food on your table."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 374201.0,
      "end_time": 377274.0,
      "text": "Even here in this hotel, the invisible ones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 377298.0,
      "end_time": 380750.0,
      "text": "the butchers, the bakers the candlestick makers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380774.0,
      "end_time": 383167.0,
      "text": "they make the machines that make your french fries"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383191.0,
      "end_time": 384417.0,
      "text": "and they make your beds."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 384441.0,
      "end_time": 387845.0,
      "text": "These are the invisible businesswomen trading across borders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 389370.0,
      "end_time": 391406.0,
      "text": "all on the side of the road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 391430.0,
      "end_time": 394348.0,
      "text": "and so they&#39;re invisible to data gatherers."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394704.0,
      "end_time": 398360.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re mashed together with the vast informal sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 398384.0,
      "end_time": 403457.0,
      "text": "that doesn&#39;t bother to distinguish between smugglers and tax evaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 403481.0,
      "end_time": 406890.0,
      "text": "and those running illegal whatnot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 406113.0,
      "end_time": 408144.0,
      "text": "and the ladies who trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 408168.0,
      "end_time": 412313.0,
      "text": "and who put food on the table and send their kids to university."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 412337.0,
      "end_time": 415562.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s really what I&#39;m asking here."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 415586.0,
      "end_time": 418421.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s all that we need to start by doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 418868.0,
      "end_time": 423477.0,
      "text": "Can we start by recognizing the skills, the occupations?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 423501.0,
      "end_time": 428125.0,
      "text": "We could transform the informal economy by beginning with this recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 428149.0,
      "end_time": 432830.0,
      "text": "and then designing the customized doorways for them to enter"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 432854.0,
      "end_time": 435630.0,
      "text": "or integrate with the formal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 435870.0,
      "end_time": 436390.0,
      "text": "with the global,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 436415.0,
      "end_time": 438126.0,
      "text": "with the entire system."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 438150.0,
      "end_time": 439714.0,
      "text": "Thank you, ladies and gentlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 439738.0,
      "end_time": 443459.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}